{"tid":386702,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新手儲蓄求救","createTime":"2017-09-04T05:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T09:18:44.000Z","uid":61967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00ad9f889e1235af58310050be2cad0199f2f874","tid":386702,"uid":61967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"第一年出嚟做嘢，想學人扮下理財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我唔敢放係自己活期acc（我一定忍唔到手用左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）。股票嗰啲高風險...自己又唔會做功課就免啦...<br />\n而家想為自己定一個短期目標：每月大概固定儲2000元，想儲1年-年半左右<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位，有咩儲蓄計劃適合我呢啲新人<br />\n同理咁多銀行，一般做儲蓄去大行定細行會好啲？<br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da5709de232d91be1430b8bc0fedda447b1fe44","tid":386702,"uid":106304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"出黎做fulltime定partime先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> fulltime嘅話每個月儲2千蚊好似真係少左d <br />\n2千蚊講真唔洗講到要理財投資咁<br />\n去間銀行開個account for扔錢落去就ok<br />\n利申番緊partime都係咁做 就快轉fulltime應該都只係買吓大股算 其餘放落唔常用嘅bank account"},{"pid":"146cf58cf57b2bee55ce41b1e9da393b9d11f8ad","tid":386702,"uid":38862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:26:51.000Z","msg":"月供股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7eab1a33ab8763535c521b706241e2699ac6ca","tid":386702,"uid":53429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:30:58.000Z","msg":"餘額寶"},{"pid":"4fac83c9e02ad29e62f9d5d69232d04aaf4a7a0e","tid":386702,"uid":60603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T06:35:17.000Z","msg":"一年至半年仲要得個2千蚊一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />